  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_042c8e08aba31b6da4cc327c477fbe2f">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes master tapes, phonograph records, and compact disks of various Cornell a cappella groups, including Cayuga's Waiters, Touchtones, Class Notes, Nothing But Treble and Hangovers.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_9efc0b0bf14f438ef2b4e85aa1ec4f75">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Also 5 digital audio tapes: commencements 1993, 1994; Cornell state of the university, 1993; and Cornell address by Dick Cheney.</p>  </scopecontent>
